\sqrt{12-\!\sqrt{12-\!\sqrt{12-\cdots}}}
=\sqrt{12-x} \quad &\mbox{where x is our answer} \\
12-x = (\sqrt{12-x})^2 \\
12 -x = 12-x \\
x= \boxed{2}
\end{align*}
